{"pagelen": 100, "values": [{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-rendering/issues/57/comments/56277087.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-rendering/issues/57#comment-56277087"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-rendering/issues/57.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 57, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-rendering.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-rendering"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{f6b404b6-f373-460d-a470-69ff6f27cd93}ts=1533308"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "ign-rendering", "full_name": "ignitionrobotics/ign-rendering", "uuid": "{f6b404b6-f373-460d-a470-69ff6f27cd93}"}, "title": "Actor animation flickering"}, "content": {"raw": "[Line 272](#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-rendering/src/ee3bdc5fbe6ece157ae73fc03af2ce9deade2079/examples/actor_animation/GlutWindow.cc#lines-272)  was causing the issue. It updated `g_time` with `steady_clock::duration()`, so in the next `updateActor()` call `seconds` became 0 and was showing the actor animation state at index 0. Following this actor pose update, because `seconds` was 0, it went to else block resulting in the correct animation pose. Hence the flickering.\n\nI have fixed this issue by updating the `g_startTime` after completion of each actor animation sequence. [PR #239](#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-rendering/pull-requests/239/fix-actor-animation-flickering)\n\n\u200c", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p><a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-rendering/src/ee3bdc5fbe6ece157ae73fc03af2ce9deade2079/examples/actor_animation/GlutWindow.cc#lines-272\" rel=\"nofollow\">Line 272</a>  was causing the issue. It updated <code>g_time</code> with <code>steady_clock::duration()</code>, so in the next <code>updateActor()</code> call <code>seconds</code> became 0 and was showing the actor animation state at index 0. Following this actor pose update, because <code>seconds</code> was 0, it went to else block resulting in the correct animation pose. Hence the flickering.</p>\n<p>I have fixed this issue by updating the <code>g_startTime</code> after completion of each actor animation sequence. <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-rendering/pull-requests/239/fix-actor-animation-flickering\" rel=\"nofollow\">PR #239</a></p>\n<p>\u200c</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2020-02-23T05:30:50.259480+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Sarathkrishnan Ramesh", "uuid": "{4863ddae-095b-4548-987b-a364c4012e01}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B4863ddae-095b-4548-987b-a364c4012e01%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B4863ddae-095b-4548-987b-a364c4012e01%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/5c9bad79203e134514cf86a8/b7e8978f-1e47-4014-ae2e-af396180f9bc/128"}}, "nickname": "sarath18", "type": "user", "account_id": "5c9bad79203e134514cf86a8"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 56277087}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-rendering/issues/57/comments/56350142.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-rendering/issues/57#comment-56350142"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-rendering/issues/57.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 57, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-rendering.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-rendering"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{f6b404b6-f373-460d-a470-69ff6f27cd93}ts=1533308"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "ign-rendering", "full_name": "ignitionrobotics/ign-rendering", "uuid": "{f6b404b6-f373-460d-a470-69ff6f27cd93}"}, "title": "Actor animation flickering"}, "content": {"raw": null, "markup": "markdown", "html": "", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2020-02-28T11:09:30.776886+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Sarathkrishnan Ramesh", "uuid": "{4863ddae-095b-4548-987b-a364c4012e01}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B4863ddae-095b-4548-987b-a364c4012e01%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B4863ddae-095b-4548-987b-a364c4012e01%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/5c9bad79203e134514cf86a8/b7e8978f-1e47-4014-ae2e-af396180f9bc/128"}}, "nickname": "sarath18", "type": "user", "account_id": "5c9bad79203e134514cf86a8"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 56350142}], "page": 1, "size": 2}